{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4099","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"變一文學路打通正式動工","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4099-1.jpeg","sequence":4099,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/17QkXzRQN6/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-10-16T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"變一文學路打通正式動工"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"變一文學路打通正式動工"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1、118 年完工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2、總經費 6.4 億，中央出 6.07 億，地方出 0.33 億。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3、文學路走地下道、從原先雙向兩車道變成雙向一車道，樂善一路僅剩步道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4、目前雅倫正在爭取樂善一路打通儘速核定，真正落實 A7 雙十字路廊。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小結：這條變一，雅倫從上一屆爭取到現在，雖然少了一條車道，但市府也聽到我們的聲音，在我不斷強調雙十字路廊的重要性之後，終於送出「樂善一路」，也就是變四的都市計劃變更。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"會中我也跟市府團隊強調，這條久等了的道路，在選舉年前終於要開工了，既然開工了，工程絕對不可以再延宕！還有承諾給龜山的公園，也絕不可以再縮水！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4099-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4099-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4099-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4099-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4099-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4099-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4099-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4099-4.jpeg"},"chil